column1: Who are you and why are you stopping me?
You're a human? Please go back. This has nothing to do with you.
You guys are definitely planning something.
I am a living god; I can't just sit idly.
I don't care if you are a living god.
All we need right now is time.
Once we are done, we will leave peacefully.
How can I just stand by!
If we continue to ignore these magical meteor fragments,
youkai might go wild and cause a rampage!
What do youkai have to do with humans?
It seems that I'll have to force my way in.
Prepare yourself for a danmaku battle!
Do you really think you can escape my volley of arrows?
Faced with this Divine Bow of Kotobiki,
